OL,3,CUS tariffs and blowing the budget
OL,4,C'among cost concerns for holidaymakers'
OL,6,FTwo-thirds (66%) of people are
OL,7,Fplanning a holiday abroad this year, a
OL,8,Freport has found.
OL,10,FBut nearly four-fifths (78%) are
OL,11,Fworried about the impact that US trade
OL,12,Ftariffs may have on prices in
OL,13,Fdestinations abroad and over half
OL,14,F(53%) plan to avoid destinations where
OL,15,Fthey believe tariffs could affect
OL,16,Fresort prices.
OL,18,FOver three-quarters (77%) said that
OL,19,Fexchange rates are a big concern for
OL,20,Fthem.
