OL,3,CUS tariffs and blowing the budget
OL,4,C'among cost concerns for holidaymakers'
OL,6,FPost Office Travel Money's Holiday
OL,7,FSpending Report also found that
OL,8,Fholidaymakers rated Spain, Turkey and
OL,9,FThailand as being the "best value for
OL,10,Fmoney" out of 39 worldwide
OL,11,Fdestinations.
OL,13,FMore than half (52%) of holidaymakers
OL,14,Fsaid they will budget more for their
OL,15,Fnext holiday due to increased costs.
OL,17,FOver four-fifths (82%) said that they
OL,18,Fhad set a budget, averaging #377, on
OL,19,Ftheir last trip.
