OL,3,CUS tariffs and blowing the budget
OL,4,C'among cost concerns for holidaymakers'
OL,6,FBut seven in 10 (71%) admitted blowing
OL,7,Ftheir budget, by #140 on average.
OL,9,FLaura Plunkett, head of travel money
OL,10,Fat the Post Office, said: "This year's
OL,11,Fholiday spending research again
OL,12,Fdemonstrates that holidaymakers don't
OL,13,Falways set a realistic budget and
OL,14,Foverspend by large amounts as a
OL,15,Fresult."
OL,17,FThe Post Office used two surveys of
OL,18,Fmore than 2,000 people, carried out in
OL,19,FApril and May, for its research.
